      "message": "[Critical] Line 507: placeCall now runs before the call view model is passed to present(...withStateable:). If placeCall can fail or transition state quickly, the coordinator may miss lifecycle/state callbacks that were previously registered before the daemon call started, leaving the call UI unpresented or cleanup unhandled. Preserve the early daemon call only after the stateable/lifecycle observer is registered, or add an explicit pre-registration API before placeCall.\n```suggestion\n        let callViewController \u003d CallViewController.instantiate(with: injectionBag)\n        registerStateable(callViewController.viewModel)\n        callViewController.viewModel.placeCall(with: contactRingId,\n                                               userName: userName,\n                                               account: account,\n                                               isAudioOnly: isAudioOnly)\n```",
